<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Mishmeret — Kashrut Yoreh De'ah</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,300;9..144,500;9..144,600;9..144,700&family=Source+Sans+3:wght@400;500;600;700&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>

  :root{
    --ink:#192a4d;
    --ink-soft:#2c3f66;
    --parchment:#f7f2e7;
    --parchment-deep:#efe7d4;
    --gold:#a9842f;
    --gold-soft:#c9a866;
    --charcoal:#262420;
    --sage:#56714f;
    --line:#d8cdb0;
    --white:#fffdf8;
    --shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(25,42,77,0.12);
  }

  *{box-sizing:border-box;}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
  body{
    margin:0;
    background:var(--parchment);
    color:var(--charcoal);
    font-family:'Source Sans 3', sans-serif;
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  }

  h1,h2,h3,h4{
    font-family:'Fraunces', serif;
    margin:0;
    color:var(--ink);
    letter-spacing:-0.01em;
  }

  .mono{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;}

  a{color:var(--ink);}

  .wrap{max-width:1140px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 28px;}

  /* ---------- NAV ---------- */
  .topbar{
    position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50;
    background:rgba(247,242,231,0.94);
    backdrop-filter:blur(6px);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .topbar-inner{
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
    padding:14px 28px;max-width:1140px;margin:0 auto;
  }
  .brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;text-decoration:none;}
  .brand img{height:38px;width:38px;display:block;}
  .brand-text{display:flex;flex-direction:column;line-height:1.05;}
  .brand-text strong{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:18px;color:var(--ink);font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.02em;}
  .brand-text span{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);font-weight:600;}

  nav.primary{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:26px;}
  nav.primary a{
    font-size:14px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;color:var(--ink-soft);
    position:relative;padding:4px 0;
  }
  nav.primary a:hover{color:var(--ink);}
  .nav-cta{
    background:var(--ink);color:var(--white);padding:9px 18px;border-radius:3px;
    font-size:13px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.02em;
    border:1px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .nav-cta:hover{background:var(--ink-soft);}
  .nav-toggle{display:none;}

  @media (max-width:880px){
    nav.primary.links{display:none;}
    .nav-toggle{display:block;background:none;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:4px;padding:8px 10px;}
  }

  /* ---------- HERO ---------- */
  .hero{
    position:relative;
    padding:72px 0 88px;
    overflow:hidden;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 85% 20%, rgba(169,132,47,0.10), transparent 55%),
      var(--parchment);
  }
  .hero-grid{
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.15fr 0.85fr;gap:56px;align-items:center;
  }
  .eyebrow{
    display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
    font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--gold);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:18px;
  }
  .eyebrow::before{content:"";width:18px;height:1px;background:var(--gold);display:inline-block;}
  .hero h1{font-size:clamp(34px,4.4vw,56px);font-weight:600;line-height:1.05;}
  .hero h1 em{font-style:normal;color:var(--gold);}
  .hero p.lead{font-size:18px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--ink-soft);margin:20px 0 0;max-width:520px;}
  .hero-meta{display:flex;gap:28px;margin-top:28px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .hero-meta div{font-size:13px;color:var(--charcoal);}
  .hero-meta strong{display:block;font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:22px;color:var(--ink);font-weight:600;}

  .seal-wrap{
    display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center;position:relative;
  }
  .seal-wrap img{width:100%;max-width:300px;filter:drop-shadow(0 18px 30px rgba(25,42,77,0.18));}

  /* Verify lookup - signature element */
  .verify-box{
    margin-top:40px;background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:6px;padding:22px 24px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);max-width:560px;
  }
  .verify-box .vb-label{
    font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);
    font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px;display:block;
  }
  .verify-row{display:flex;gap:10px;}
  .verify-row input{
    flex:1;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:4px;padding:12px 14px;
    font-size:15px;font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;background:var(--parchment);
  }
  .verify-row input:focus{outline:2px solid var(--gold-soft);outline-offset:1px;}
  .verify-row button{
    background:var(--ink);color:var(--white);border:none;border-radius:4px;
    padding:0 20px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;font-size:14px;
  }
  .verify-row button:hover{background:var(--ink-soft);}
  #verifyResults{margin-top:14px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;}
  .verify-hit{
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;
    padding:10px 12px;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:4px;background:var(--parchment);
    font-size:14px;
  }
  .verify-hit .vh-name{font-weight:600;color:var(--ink);}
  .verify-hit .vh-meta{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-soft);}
  .stamp{
    display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;
    text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.06em;padding:4px 9px;border-radius:20px;
  }
  .stamp.active{background:rgba(86,113,79,0.14);color:var(--sage);}
  .stamp.pending{background:rgba(169,132,47,0.16);color:var(--gold);}
  .verify-empty{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-soft);padding:6px 2px;}

  /* ---------- SECTION SHELL ---------- */
  section{padding:88px 0;}
  .section-head{max-width:680px;margin:0 0 44px;}
  .section-head .eyebrow{margin-bottom:14px;}
  .section-head h2{font-size:clamp(28px,3.2vw,38px);font-weight:600;}
  .section-head p{font-size:16px;color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.6;margin-top:14px;}

  .alt{background:var(--white);border-top:1px solid var(--line);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);}

  /* ---------- ABOUT ---------- */
  .about-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:48px;align-items:start;}
  .about-grid p{line-height:1.75;color:var(--charcoal);font-size:15.5px;margin:0 0 16px;}
  .rabbi-card{
    border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:6px;padding:24px;background:var(--parchment);
    display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start;margin-top:20px;
  }
  .rabbi-card img{width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;object-fit:contain;background:var(--white);padding:2px;border:1px solid var(--line);}
  .rabbi-card h4{font-size:15px;margin-bottom:4px;}
  .rabbi-card span{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-soft);}
  .timeline{border-left:2px solid var(--gold-soft);padding-left:22px;margin-top:10px;}
  .timeline .t-item{margin-bottom:18px;position:relative;}
  .timeline .t-item::before{
    content:"";position:absolute;left:-28px;top:4px;width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:50%;
    background:var(--gold);border:2px solid var(--parchment);
  }
  .timeline .t-year{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;color:var(--gold);font-weight:600;}
  .timeline .t-text{font-size:14.5px;color:var(--charcoal);margin-top:2px;}

  /* ---------- STANDARDS ---------- */
  .standards-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:18px;}
  .standard-card{
    border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:6px;padding:24px 20px;background:var(--white);
    position:relative;
  }
  .standard-card::before{
    content:"";position:absolute;top:14px;right:14px;width:8px;height:8px;border:1px solid var(--gold);
    transform:rotate(45deg);
  }
  .standard-card .s-mark{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;color:var(--gold);font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.06em;}
  .standard-card h4{font-size:17px;margin:10px 0 8px;}
  .standard-card p{font-size:13.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.55;margin:0;}

  /* ---------- DIRECTORY ---------- */
  .dir-controls{display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:22px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .dir-controls input, .dir-controls select{
    border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:4px;padding:10px 12px;font-size:14px;
    font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;background:var(--white);
  }
  .dir-controls input{flex:1;min-width:220px;}
  table.dir{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;}
  table.dir thead th{
    text-align:left;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--ink-soft);background:var(--parchment-deep);padding:12px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  table.dir tbody td{padding:13px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);font-size:14px;vertical-align:middle;}
  table.dir tbody tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none;}
  table.dir tbody tr:hover{background:rgba(169,132,47,0.05);}
  .est-name{font-weight:600;color:var(--ink);}
  .est-cat{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-soft);}
  .cert-id{font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-soft);}
  .dir-note{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-top:14px;}

  /* ---------- RESOURCES ---------- */
  .resources-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:18px;}
  .resource-card{
    border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:6px;padding:22px;background:var(--white);
    text-decoration:none;display:block;transition:border-color .15s, transform .15s;
  }
  .resource-card:hover{border-color:var(--gold);transform:translateY(-2px);}
  .resource-card .r-tag{
    font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);font-weight:700;
  }
  .resource-card h4{font-size:16px;margin:8px 0 6px;color:var(--ink);}
  .resource-card p{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-soft);margin:0;line-height:1.5;}
  .resource-card .r-go{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-top:12px;display:inline-block;font-weight:600;}

  /* ---------- FORMS ---------- */
  .forms-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:28px;}
  .form-card{border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:6px;background:var(--white);overflow:hidden;}
  .form-card-head{padding:20px 22px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--parchment-deep);}
  .form-card-head h3{font-size:18px;}
  .form-card-head p{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-soft);margin:6px 0 0;}
  .form-card-body{padding:22px;}
  .mock-field{margin-bottom:14px;}
  .mock-field label{display:block;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-bottom:6px;}
  .mock-field input, .mock-field select, .mock-field textarea{
    width:100%;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:4px;padding:10px 12px;font-size:14px;
    font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;background:var(--parchment);
  }
  .mock-submit{
    background:var(--ink);color:var(--white);border:none;border-radius:4px;padding:11px 20px;
    font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;font-size:14px;margin-top:4px;
  }
  .form-note{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-top:12px;line-height:1.5;}
  .cognito-slot{
    border:1px dashed var(--gold-soft);border-radius:4px;padding:16px;text-align:center;
    font-size:12.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);background:var(--parchment);margin-bottom:14px;
  }

  /* ---------- NEWSLETTER ---------- */
  .newsletter{
    background:var(--ink);color:var(--white);border-radius:8px;padding:44px;
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:32px;flex-wrap:wrap;
  }
  .newsletter h3{color:var(--white);font-size:24px;}
  .newsletter p{color:#c9d2e6;font-size:14px;margin:8px 0 0;max-width:380px;}
  .newsletter-form{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .newsletter-form input{
    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);background:rgba(255,255,255,0.07);color:var(--white);
    border-radius:4px;padding:12px 14px;font-size:14px;min-width:240px;
  }
  .newsletter-form input::placeholder{color:#9fabc9;}
  .newsletter-form button{
    background:var(--gold);color:var(--ink);border:none;border-radius:4px;padding:0 20px;
    font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;font-size:14px;
  }

  /* ---------- CONTACT / FOOTER ---------- */
  .contact-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:48px;}
  .contact-item{display:flex;gap:14px;margin-bottom:20px;}
  .contact-item .ci-icon{
    width:38px;height:38px;border:1px solid var(--gold-soft);border-radius:50%;display:flex;
    align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--gold);font-weight:700;font-size:14px;flex-shrink:0;
  }
  .contact-item h4{font-size:14.5px;margin-bottom:3px;}
  .contact-item span{font-size:14px;color:var(--ink-soft);}

  footer{background:var(--ink);color:#c9d2e6;padding:48px 0 28px;}
  .footer-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.4fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:32px;margin-bottom:36px;}
  .footer-brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:12px;}
  .footer-brand img{width:34px;height:34px;}
  .footer-brand strong{color:var(--white);font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:17px;}
  footer p.fdesc{font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:#9fabc9;max-width:280px;}
  footer h5{color:var(--white);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:14px;font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;font-weight:700;}
  footer ul{list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;}
  footer a{color:#c9d2e6;text-decoration:none;font-size:13.5px;}
  footer a:hover{color:var(--gold-soft);}
  .footer-bottom{
    border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);padding-top:20px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;
    font-size:12px;color:#7e8caf;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;
  }

  @media (max-width:900px){
    .hero-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .seal-wrap{order:-1;margin-bottom:10px;}
    .about-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .standards-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}
    .resources-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;}
    .forms-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .contact-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .footer-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;}
  }
  @media (max-width:560px){
    .standards-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .resources-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .hero-meta{gap:18px;}
    table.dir{font-size:12px;}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ============ NAV ============ -->
<div class="topbar">
  <div class="topbar-inner">
    <a href="#home" class="brand">
      <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Mishmeret seal">
      <div class="brand-text">
        <strong>MISHMERET</strong>
        <span>Kashrut Yoreh De'ah</span>
      </div>
    </a>
    <nav class="primary links">
      <a href="#about">About</a>
      <a href="#standards">Standards</a>
      <a href="#directory">Directory</a>
      <a href="#resources">Resources</a>
      <a href="#apply">Apply</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
    <a href="#apply" class="nav-cta">Apply for Certification</a>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
<section class="hero" id="home" style="padding-top:56px;">
  <div class="wrap hero-grid">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">Sephardic Kashrut Supervision</span>
      <h1>Trusted certification,<br>under the <em>presidency of</em><br>Rabbi David Navarro.</h1>
      <p class="lead">Mishmeret provides Sephardic kashrut supervision and certification for restaurants, caterers, groceries and food manufacturers across New York, New Jersey and the surrounding areas — built on the standards of Yoreh De'ah.</p>

      <div class="hero-meta">
        <div><strong>140+</strong>Certified establishments</div>
        <div><strong>NY · NJ</strong>Service area &amp; surrounding</div>
        <div><strong>1987</strong>Serving the community since</div>
      </div>

      <div class="verify-box">
        <span class="vb-label">Verify a certified establishment</span>
        <div class="verify-row">
          <input type="text" id="verifyInput" placeholder="Search by establishment name or cert ID…" autocomplete="off">
          <button onclick="runVerify()">Verify</button>
        </div>
        <div id="verifyResults"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="seal-wrap">
      <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Mishmeret official seal">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ ABOUT ============ -->
<section id="about" class="alt">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Who we are</span>
      <h2>A focused hashgacha, built on trust.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div>
        <p>Mishmeret began as Congregation Medrashdavid's local kashrut committee, formally established to give Sephardic families in the tri-state area a hashgacha they could rely on without ambiguity.</p>
        <p>In 2022, the organization rebranded from <strong>KMD Kashrus</strong> to <strong>Mishmeret</strong> — a name chosen to reflect a renewed commitment to higher, clearly documented standards, and to avoid confusion with an unrelated organization using similar initials abroad. As part of the transition, every certified account and establishment was individually re-audited before being re-issued under the new seal.</p>
        <p>We remain intentionally focused: a small, hands-on supervisory team rather than a sprawling national network — so every certified kitchen is one our mashgichim actually know.</p>

        <div class="rabbi-card">
          <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Rabbi David Navarro">
          <div>
            <h4>Rabbi David Navarro, sh"lita</h4>
            <span>Rabbinic President &amp; Head of the Beis Din of Mishmeret, overseeing all certification standards and final psak on questions of kashrus.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:6px;">Organizational timeline</h4>
        <div class="timeline">
          <div class="t-item"><div class="t-year">1987</div><div class="t-text">Founded as the kashrut committee of Congregation Medrashdavid, serving local Sephardic families.</div></div>
          <div class="t-item"><div class="t-year">2009</div><div class="t-text">Formalized as an independent certifying body: KMD Kashrus.</div></div>
          <div class="t-item"><div class="t-year">2022</div><div class="t-text">Rebranded to Mishmeret; full account audit and re-certification of every establishment.</div></div>
          <div class="t-item"><div class="t-year">2026</div><div class="t-text">Now supervising 140+ restaurants, caterers, groceries and manufacturers across NY &amp; NJ.</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ STANDARDS ============ -->
<section id="standards">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Our standards</span>
      <h2>Certification rooted in Yoreh De'ah.</h2>
      <p>Every Mishmeret certification is issued against a documented set of halachic standards, reviewed by our Beis Din and verified through unannounced inspection visits.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="standards-grid">
      <div class="standard-card">
        <span class="s-mark">YD · 01</span>
        <h4>Bishul Yisrael</h4>
        <p>All cooking on the premises supervised so that a Jew has a direct role in the cooking process, per the standards of Yoreh De'ah.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="standard-card">
        <span class="s-mark">YD · 02</span>
        <h4>Yoshon Compliance</h4>
        <p>Grain-based products are verified against current Yoshon listings before approval for use in certified kitchens.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="standard-card">
        <span class="s-mark">YD · 03</span>
        <h4>Chalav Yisrael Option</h4>
        <p>Establishments may certify under Chalav Yisrael or Chalav Stam; status is clearly disclosed on every certificate.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="standard-card">
        <span class="s-mark">YD · 04</span>
        <h4>Unannounced Inspection</h4>
        <p>Mashgichim conduct routine, unscheduled visits — logged in our internal inspection registry for every certified site.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ DIRECTORY ============ -->
<section id="directory" class="alt">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Certified establishments</span>
      <h2>The Mishmeret directory.</h2>
      <p>Search certified restaurants, caterers, groceries and manufacturers currently under our supervision. Sample listing shown below.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="dir-controls">
      <input type="text" id="dirSearch" placeholder="Search establishments…" onkeyup="filterDirectory()">
      <select id="dirCategory" onchange="filterDirectory()">
        <option value="">All categories</option>
        <option value="Restaurant">Restaurant</option>
        <option value="Caterer">Caterer</option>
        <option value="Grocery">Grocery</option>
        <option value="Bakery">Bakery</option>
        <option value="Manufacturer">Manufacturer</option>
      </select>
    </div>

    <table class="dir">
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Establishment</th><th>Category</th><th>Location</th><th>Cert ID</th><th>Last Inspection</th><th>Status</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody id="dirBody"></tbody>
    </table>
    <p class="dir-note">Directory shown with sample data for demonstration. Live version will sync with the internal inspection database.</p>
  </div>
